## 🏗️ System Architecture

NEXUS AI adheres to a modular design philosophy, separating concerns between state, processing logic, external services, and representation layers:

┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                         UIRenderer                          │
│         (Custom CSS Injector & Streamlit Interface)        │
└──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────┘
│ User Input / Streamlit Rerun
┌──────────────────────────────▼──────────────────────────────┐
│                        CommandRouter                        │
│     (Dialogue FSM Override + Intent Pattern Regex Matcher)   │
└──────┬───────────────────────┬───────────────────────┬──────┘
│                       │                       │
┌──────▼───────┐        ┌──────▼───────┐        ┌──────▼───────┐
│ WeatherServ. │        │   ToolBox    │        │  DataManager │
│ (Geocoding / │        │ (Stateless   │        │ (In-Memory   │
│ Meteo API)   │        │ Computations)│        │ CRUD Lists)  │
└──────┬───────┘        └──────┬───────┘        └──────┬───────┘
│                       │                       │
┌──────┴───────────────────────┴───────────────────────┴──────┐
│                 SessionManager & RateLimiter                │
│            (Timestamps / Session State Storage)             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘


* **`SessionManager`:** Boots, updates, and trims dialogue history to a maximum window of 200 responses to prevent memory leaks.
* **`CommandRouter`:** Manages active multi-step operations using a finite state machine layout (`dialogue_mode`) alongside classic Regex keyword identification layers.
* **`ToolBox`:** Houses pure arithmetic calculations completely free of Streamlit UI dependencies or tracking side effects.
* **`UIRenderer`:** Injects custom dark-mode styled HTML structures into native Streamlit blocks to produce a custom look and feel.

