## 🛠️ Installation & Setup

### Prerequisites
Make sure you have Python 3.8+ installed on your operating system.

### 1. Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone [https://github.com/yourusername/nexus-ai.git](https://github.com/yourusername/nexus-ai.git)
cd nexus-ai
2. Install Dependencies
Install the required packages using pip:

Bash
pip install streamlit requests
(Optional: Install psutil if you want live CPU, RAM, and Disk hardware metrics via the system command)

Bash
pip install psutil
3. Run the Application
Execute the Streamlit framework pointing to the main file:

Bash
streamlit run Rule_based_AI_Chatbot.py
📖 Sample Commands
Simply type any of the following directly into the chat input field:

help — Brings up the complete interactive menu block.

weather — Prompts the system to fetch conditions for a specific city.

add or multiply — Triggers step-by-step math workflows.

todo / todo view / todo done 1 — Interface with the productivity system.

expense — Record a monetary entry.

quote — Displays a randomized professional programming or philosophical quote.

system — Inspect internal execution architecture performance (OS, Python version, hardware load).

